  entryName: Pasatsat
  entryDescription: Is that a person wrapped in a mat?
  entryLore: "A reed mat on the trail blocked my path, and I felt the air choked.
    It\u2019s the ghost of a burial that never got a proper coffin. It\u2019s best
    to cut through the center with a blade. When it died, the mat opened to reveal
    nothing but a putrid smell."
